\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 2.\tab}Thou shalt not make any graven image, or bow down before any 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 3.\tab}creation in heaven or on earth. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 4.\tab}Thou shalt not take the name of the Lord in vain. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 5.\tab}Remember the Sabbath day and keep it holy. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 6.\tab}Honor thy father and thy mother. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 7.\tab}Thou shalt not kill. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 8.\tab}Thou shalt not commit adultery. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 9.\tab}Thou shalt not steal. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 10.\tab}Thou shalt not bear false witness against thy neighbor. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 11.\tab}Thou shalt not covet that which is thy neighbors. 
