\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 3.\tab}To fast and to abstain on the days appointed by the Church. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\insrsid2454493 \hich\af0\dbch\af0\loch\f0 4.\tab}To confess our sins and to receive the Holy Mysteries at least 
