\s52\ql \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid2454493 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\cs56\b\insrsid2454493 QUESTIONS TO ASK YOURSELF TO PREPARE FOR CONFESSION}{
\insrsid2454493  
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}}\pard\plain \ql \fi-360\li720\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar\jclisttab\tx720\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls4\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0\pararsid2454493 
\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid2454493 Have you prayed to God upon rising and before eating and sleeping? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}During prayer were you distracted by other thoughts? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Did you make the sign of the Cross carelessly? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you attended Church services regularly? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}When in Church, have you been inattentive, laughed or talked 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}unnecessarily? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you used the name of the Lord in swearing or in a joking 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}way? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you sworn or murmured against God? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you been ashamed to make the sign of the Cross in front 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}of others? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you attended parties, movies, etc. during the hours of 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Church services? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you failed to keep the fast or other rules of the Church? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you believed in astrology, superstitions, fortune-tellers 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}or the like? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you strayed from the teachings of the Church by unbelief 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}or indifference to the Faith? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you failed to ask for God's help in every effort? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you concealed sins at confession? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Do you show your parents proper respect? Have you been rude 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}to them, talked back or otherwise offended them? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}If your parents are reposed, have you prayed for them. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you been disrespectful to members of the clergy, your 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}elders, teachers or superiors? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you been angry or irritated? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you abused anyone? Used foul language? Struck someone? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Offended someone in an argument? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you raised your voice in anger? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you joked or made fun of the handicapped, unfortunate, 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}or elderly? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Are you truly at peace with everyone? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you asked forgiveness of those you may have offended? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you failed to give aid to someone in need, especially 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}when asked? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you donated to the needs of the Church? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you been cruel to animals? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you taken something without asking? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you failed to return a book or other thing that you have 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}borrowed? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you been stubborn, insistent on pressing your point of 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}view? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you plotted or taken revenge on one who's offended you? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you told falsehoods, distorted the truth, cheated, judged 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}others or gossiped? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you joked of the faults of others, or exposed the faults 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}of another to make yourself the better? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you been vain? Sought glory or praise for yourself? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Does your inner peace disappear when others are unfair to 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}you or judge you? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Are you proud? Do you brag of your abilities, position or 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}possessions? Do you consider yourself worthy or sinless in the 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}sight of God? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you been overly concerned with your appearance? Are you 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}properly attired in God's house? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}The 7th commandment includes all sins of a sexual nature, 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}either by thought, word, or deed, any of these must be confessed. 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you been envious of another's possessions, appearance 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}or standing? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you fulfilled all obligations faithfully? Have you been 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}lazy? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Have you been impatient? Fallen into despair or apathy? Had 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}thoughts of suicide? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Are you attached to smoking, alcohol, or other drugs? Food 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}or drink? 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\f3\fs20\insrsid2454493 \loch\af3\dbch\af0\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}Do you give up your heart to money or other earthly possessions? 
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid2454493 {\insrsid3211628\charrsid2454493 
\par }}